    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I noticed in https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/5844 that the changelog for CISA was using the correct URL, but not the one for Vue InstantSearch. The only difference I see that could matter was that in their respective `package.json` files, CISA has \"algolia/instantsearch\" in the repository field, whereas Vue has \"https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js\".\r\n\r\nSo I guess your changes will fix changelog generation next time!",
